ng%20when%20I%20arrived%20other%20than%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20off%20the%20train%20in%20Venice%2C%20I%20had%20enough%20energy%20to%20explore%20since%20I%20had%20gotten%20some%20sleep%20in%20the%20bunk%2C%20but%20I%20still%20felt%20fatigued%2C%20and%20it%20took%20away%20from%20how%20much%20I%20could%20enjoy%20that%20first%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20my%20first%20day%20in%20both%20cities%20felt%20disappointing%2C%20and%20my%20plan%20to%20save%20time%20and%20energy%20backfired.%20I%20couldn't%20help%20thinking%20I%20wasted%20two%20days%20that%20could%20have%20been%20spent%20feeling%20more%20appreciative%20of%20the%20city%20surrounding%20me%20had%20I%20gotten%20enough%20rest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20trip%20was%20more%20physically%20draining%20than%20I%20anticipated%20because%20my%20backpack%20made%20my%20body%20sore.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20images%3A%20Left%3A%20The%20author%20walks%20next%20to%20a%20train%20wearing%20a%20big%20backpack.%20Right%3A%20The%20author%20sits%20in%20a%20train%20seat%20stretching%20her%20neck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64148f7a5f4f5400191a1862%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20sores%20her%20back%20from%20carrying%20her%20bag.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20travel%20days%2C%20I%20had%20to%20carry%20my%20backpack%20for%20long%20periods.%20I%20wore%20it%20on%20the%20go%20to%20catch%20my%20train.%20When%20I%20arrived%20in%20a%20new%20city%2C%20I%20had%20to%20keep%20it%20on%20my%20back%20until%20I%20could%20check%20into%20my%20accommodation.%20And%20then%2C%20I'd%20repeat%20the%20entire%20process%20when%20I%20checked%20out%20before%20catching%20a%20train%20to%20my%20next%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20day%2C%20after%20wearing%20my%20backpack%20while%20walking%20f