ehind%20that%20choice%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJon%20M.%20Chu%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I'm%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20%26quot%3BBatman%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Tim%20Burton%20version%2C%20so%20I%20love%20a%20cold%20open.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20show%20that%20the%20Yellow%20Brick%20Road%20that%20we%20think%20of%20that's%20so%20iconic%20actually%20had%20to%20be%20built%20by%20somebody%2C%20or%20some%20animals.%20That%20it%20was%20not%20just%20this%20pristine%20idea.%20That%20the%20building%20of%20it%20was%20poisoned%2C%20and%20that%20Elphaba%20was%20this%20badass%20who%2C%20on%20her%20own%2C%20had%20this%20mission%20to%20free%20the%20animals%20and%20expose%20the%20truth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20main%20characters%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wizard%20of%20Oz%26quot%3B%20appear%20this%20time%20around%2C%20though%20you%20only%20show%20Dorothy%20in%20far%20shots%2C%20silhouettes%2C%20or%20just%20her%20feet.%20How%20tempting%20was%20it%20to%20shoot%20her%20face%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20opportunities%20to%20show%20more%2C%20and%20we%20shot%20some%20things%20where%20you%20could%20see%20her%20face%2C%20but%20our%20intention%2C%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20was%20not%20to%20show%20her%20face.%20But%20was%20I%20sure%20of%20that%20choice%3F%20We%20did%20get%20options%20for%20it%2C%20but%20every%20time%2C%20it%20was%20a%20distraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20we%20went%20by%20the%20whole%20time%20was%20something%20from%20the%20stage%20show.%20They%20told%20us%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20the%20girls!%26quot%3B%20Whatever%20is%20happening%2C%20it's%20about%20the%20girls.%20So%20every%20time%20it%20drew%20us%20to%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20does%20Dorothy%20think%3F%26quot%3B%20we%20reminded%20ourselves%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEven%20though%20the%20plan%20was%20to%20show%20a%20limited%20amount%20of%20Dorothy%2C%20was%20it%20still%20a%20long%20audition%20process%20to%20cast%20the%20role%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOh%2C%20yeah.%20At%20the%20auditions%2C%20we%20would%20put%20a%20sheet%20up%2C%20looking%20at%20the%20performer's%20silhouette.%20Through%20that%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20at%20how%20she%20could%20walk%2C%20but%20also%2C%20could%20I%20guide%20her%20in%20that%20way%3F%20The%20person%20had%20to%20have%20youthful%20energy%2C%20so%20we%20ultimately%20chose%20a%20dancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20dancer's%20name%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBethany%20Weaver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20also%20get%20a%20cameo%20from%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fassistant-euphoria-actor-colman-domingo-best-boss-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EColman%20Domingo.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20How%20did%20he%20come%20to%20play%20the%20Cowardly%20Lion%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20this%20amazing%20team%20of%20movement%20actors%20on%20set%20playing%20the%20animals%2C%20but%20we%20always%20knew%20we%20would%20replace%20their%20voices.%20There%20was%20a%20point%20this%20past%20year%20where%20we%20were%20cutting%20the%20movie%20together%20and%20we%20needed%20the%20voice%20because%20it%20was%20throwing%20me%20off.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20bunch%20of%20names%2C%20but%20I%20kept%20seeing%20Colman%20on%20the%20award%20circuit.%20And%20I%20felt%20he%20would%20be%20really%20fun.%20So%20I%20DMed%20him.%20I%20don't%20even%20have%20his%20phone%20number.%20I%20DMed%20him%20on%20Instagram%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%20Colman%2C%20I%20know%20we've%20met%20a%20couple%20of%20times%2C%20but%20there's%20this%20role%20of%20the%20Cowardly%20Lion%2C%20there's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20lines%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20iconic.%26quot%3B%20And%20he%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20the%20fuck%20not.%26quot%3B%20So%20we%20did%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20did%20he%20work%20on%20the%20movie%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20in%20for%20a%20day%2C%20and%20we%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20with%20it.%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20the%20character%20would%20sound.%20It%20was%20very%20collaborative.%20I%20told%20him%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20tell%20you%20anything%2C%20let's%20just%20do%20the%20scene.%26quot%3B%20And%20we%20did%20it%20over%20and%20over%20until%20we%20found%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296ed3bfa-726a-449b-aee5-1542fb05bb11%5C%22%3EOn%20staging%20that%20Elphaba%2FGlinda%20fight%20for%20the%20big%20screen%20and%20his%20favorite%20set%20piece%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225845%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Glinda%20and%20Elphaba%20squaring%20off%20on%20the%20yellow%20brick%20road%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691f080fe1a9cbb014de963c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223611%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Ariana%20Grande%20and%20Cynthia%20Erivo%20in%20%26quot%3BWicked%3A%20For%20Good.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EGiles%20Keyte%2FUniversal%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20scene%20with%20Elphaba%20and%20Glinda%20having%20their%20spat%20on%20the%20Yellow%20Brick%20Road%20post-tornado%20is%20a%20highlight%20because%20it%20plays%20with%20the%20darker%20tone%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20yet%20it's%20playful%20enough%20to%20indicate%20they%20are%20still%20friends.%20How%20did%20you%20develop%20that%20sequence%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20the%20center%20of%20our%20movie%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20difficult%20and%20how%20technical%20it%20was%20for%20these%20two%20women%20to%20navigate%20our%20tone.%20I%20never%20called%20the%20movie%20darker%3B%20I%20called%20it%20deeper.%20I%20think%20the%20power%20of%20the%20musical%20isn't%20the%20song%20and%20dance%20razzle-dazzle.%20I%20think%2C%20if%20done%20right%2C%20it%20gives%20you%20access%20inside%20their%20minds.%20You%20get%20closer%20and%20more%20intimate%20in%20the%20emotions%20of%20the%20characters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20for%20this%20moment%2C%20though%20there's%20song%20and%20dance%2C%20we%20had%20permission%20to%20get%20closer%20to%20them%20because%20of%20the%20journey%20we've%20taken%20with%20them%20to%20this%20point.%20So%2C%20yes%2C%20you%20get%20the%20nod%20of%20the%20tornado%2C%20the%20falling%20house%2C%20Dorothy%2C%20you%20get%20the%20fun%20of%20that.%20But%20if%20you%20watch%20Ariana%20Grande's%20face%2C%20watch%20when%20she%20turns%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20personal%20to%20her.%20Nessarose%20was%20a%20person%20she%20knew%20that%20turned%20wicked%20that%20has%20passed%20away%2C%20and%20it%20might%20be%20her%20fault.%20But%20she%20can't%20show%20that.%20Then%20comes%20in%20Elphaba%2C%20and%20they%20are%20both%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20Nessarose.%20And%20then%20that%20transitions%20from%20a%20real%20fight%20to%20jokes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20moment%20when%20I%20thought%20the%20fight%20wouldn't%20work%20in%20the%20movie.%20The%20jokes%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bfarm%20girl%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bhouse%20falling%20on%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20those%20are%20all%20jokes%20in%20the%20show%2C%20but%20in%20the%20movie%20they%20play%20stronger.%20And%20then%20when%20the%20slap%20happens.%20We%20kept%20it%20all%20in%20because%20we%20came%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20only%20way%20these%20two%20can%20communicate%20is%20how%20they%20did%20as%20kids%2C%20which%20was%20fighting.%20So%20even%20though%20it's%20a%20fight%2C%20it's%20a%20connecting%20point%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221537%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cynthia%20Erivo%20Ariana%20Grande%20Jon%20M%20Chu%20talking%20on%20the%20set%20of%20Wicked%20For%20Good%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691f09cce1a9cbb014de9656%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221310%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Cynthia%20Erivo%2C%20Ariana%20Grande%2C%20and%20Jon%20M.%20Chu%20on%20the%20set%20of%20%26quot%3BWicked%3A%20For%20Good.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EGiles%20Keyte%2FUniversal%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20your%20favorite%20set%20piece%20in%20%26quot%3BWicked%3A%20For%20Good%26quot%3B%3F%20One%20you%20feel%20you%20knocked%20out%20of%20the%20park.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20%26quot%3BFor%20Good%26quot%3B%20musical%20number.%20The%20restraint%20that%20both%20of%20the%20girls%20earned%20from%20both%20movies%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20%26quot%3BFor%20Good%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20doing%20the%20big%20flashy%20ending%2C%20but%20make%20it%20so%20intimate.%20Because%20ultimately%2C%20what%20the%20movie%20is%20about%20is%20giving%20them%20the%20steering%20wheel%2C%20to%20have%20them%20earn%20the%20moment.%20To%20me%2C%20that%20was%20one%20of%20my%20proudest%20moments.%20We%20even%20revisit%20%26quot%3BDefying%20Gravity%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20%26quot%3BFor%20Good%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20could%20have%20been%20a%20no-no%20%E2%80%94%20and%20believe%20me%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20conversations%20and%20debates%20to%20do%20that%20%E2%80%94%20but%20because%20it's%20coming%20from%20a%20place%20of%20her%20strength%2C%20it%20allows%20us%20to%20go%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20then%20you%20have%20to%20get%20right%20the%20lead-up%20of%20Dorothy's%20entrance%20to%20destroy%20Elphaba.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20scene%20is%20the%20most%20emotional%20pivot%20point%20of%20the%20movie.%20The%20shot%20of%20Elphaba%20outside%20of%20the%20closet%20and%20Glinda%20in%20it%2C%20that%20was%20not%20scripted%3B%20they%20did%20that%20in%20rehearsals.%20I%20was%20weeping%20when%20I%20saw%20them%20do%20that.%20I%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20put%20it%20in%20the%20movie.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20that%20comes%20from%20understanding%20the%20characters%20and%20their%20journey%2C%20and%20then%20us%20taking%20a%20bet%20it%20would%20work.%20And%20even%20when%20we%20shot%20it%2C%20the%20shot%20of%20the%20door%20between%20the%20two%20of%20them%2C%20I%20had%20to%20take%20out%20a%20wall%20to%20get%20the%20shot.%20The%20production%20designers%20were%20freaking%20out%20because%20if%20you%20take%20out%20that%20wall%2C%20that%20set%2C%20you%20can't%20shoot%20anymore.%20We%20couldn't%20come%20back%20to%20that%20set.%20And%20I%20was%20like%2C%20screw%20it%2C%20it's%20worth%20it.%20This%20is%20the%20moment.%20We%20had%20to%20go%20into%20the%20darkness%2C%20not%20knowing%20the%20answer.%20Just%20trusting%20our%20instincts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201f5ce92-cacf-49e9-821c-49dd425dc244%5C%22%3EOn%20tweaking%20the%20Wicked%20Witch's%20death%20scene%20and%20hiding%20the%20movie's%20final%20shot%20from%20Universal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221825%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tin%20Man%20Dorothy%20Lion%20Scarcrow%20meeting%20Oz%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691f0b00abd5e944effb1c02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221217%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BWicked%3A%20For%20Good.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EUniversal%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETalk%20about%20the%20POV%20shot%20of%20Glinda%20inside%20the%20closet%2C%20seeing%20Elphaba's%20demise.%20How%20did%20you%20get%20there%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20storyboarded%2C%20but%20I%20never%20stick%20to%20it.%20It's%20pretty%20different%20from%20the%20storyboard.%20When%20you%20have%20Ariana%20and%20Cynthia%20and%20they%20are%20living%20in%20these%20characters%2C%20you%20have%20to%20listen%20to%20what%20the%20movie%20is%20telling%20you.%20The%20show%20does%20the%20Dorothy%20silhouette%20for%20the%20Elphaba%20melting%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20always%20brilliant.%20We%20know%20the%20melting%2C%20but%20to%20see%20it%20through%20a%20new%20perspective%2C%20to%20actually%20enter%20the%20closet%20Glinda%20is%20hiding%20in%2C%20it%20just%20plays%20the%20whole%20scene%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20close%20up%20of%20Dorothy's%20fe