ider.com%2Fmost-overrated-us-tourist-attractions-according-to-frequent-traveler%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anthropic%20unveils%20new%20Claude%20Opus%204.5%2C%20its%20'most%20intelligent'%20model%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224503%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%C2%A0at%20the%20INBOUND%202025%20Powered%20by%20HubSpot%20at%20Moscone%20Center%20in%20San%20Francisco%20on%20September%204%2C%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691af115e1a9cbb014de5072%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223002%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20says%20he's%20uneasy%20that%20a%20few%20unelected%20tech%20leaders%20hold%20the%20power%20to%20shape%20humanity's%20AI%20future.%3Cp%3EChance%20Yeh%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20HubSpot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20launched%20Claude%20Opus%204.5%2C%20calling%20it%20its%20most%20advanced%20and%20intelligent%20AI%20model%20to%20date.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EClaude%20Opus%204.5%20excels%20at%20generating%20code%2C%20spreadsheets%2C%20and%20workplace%20documents%20for%20users.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20is%20seeking%20new%20funding%20from%20Google%2C%20potentially%20raising%20its%20valuation%20to%20%24350%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-nvidia-microsoft-azure-investment-deal-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20once%20again%20raising%20the%20bar%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20company%20unveiled%20Claude%20Opus%204.5%2C%20which%20it%20calls%20its%20most%20advanced%20AI%20model%20yet%2C%20just%20three%20months%20after%20its%20previous%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20says%20the%20latest%20version%20delivers%20major%20improvements%20in%20generating%20computer%20code%20and%20workplace%20documents%2C%20such%20as%20Excel%20spreadsheets%20and%20PowerPoint%20presentations.%20It%20also%20includes%20new%20capabilities%20for%20creating%20more%20sophisticated%2C%20long-running%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20most%20intelligent%20model%20in%20the%20world%20for%20the%20things%20that%20we%20really%20care%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Alex%20Albert%2C%20Anthropic's%20head%20of%20developer%20relations%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20completes%20the%20Claude%204.5%20family%2C%20following%20recent%20updates%20to%20the%20Sonnet%20and%20Haiku%20models.%20Opus%20models%20are%20built%20for%20advanced%20reasoning%20and%20complex%20problem-solving%2C%20while%20Sonnet%20and%20Haiku%20are%20optimized%20for%20speed%20and%20efficiency.%20It%20also%20comes%20a%20week%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffun-video-games-google-gemini-3-ai-model-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20debuted%20its%20Gemini%203%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic's%20Claude%20models%20are%20primarily%20designed%20for%20business%20users.%20A%20July%20report%20from%20Menlo%20Ventures%20found%20that%20Anthropic%20now%20leads%20in%20enterprise%20AI%20adoption%2C%20capturing%2032%25%20of%20the%20market.%20That%20puts%20it%20ahead%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20which%20holds%2025%25%E2%80%94about%20half%20of%20its%20share%20from%20two%20years%20ago.%20Google%20followed%20with%2020%25%2C%20and%20Meta%20came%20in%20fourth%20at%209%25.%20(Menlo%20Ventures%20is%20an%20investor%20in%20Anthropic).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Albert%20declined%20to%20make%20direct%20comparisons%20to%20competitors%2C%20he%20said%20Opus%204.5%20was%20designed%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bhardest%20tasks%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20intelligence-demanding%20experiences.%26quot%3B%20The%20model%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20can%20now%20generate%20spreadsheets%20of%20%26quot%3Bexpert%20human-level%20quality%26quot%3B%20similar%20to%20those%20used%20by%20financial%20an