%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-05T142603.207-1757062577-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-05T142603.207-1757062577-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-05T142603.207-1757062577-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496844%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESandhya%20Narasimhan%20is%20a%20Thane-based%20clinical%20nutritionist%20and%20lactation%20counsellor.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Sandhya%20Narasimhan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScience%20supports%20their%20claims%3A%20microgreens%20can%20hold%20up%20to%2040%20times%20more%20nutrients%20than%20mature%20vegetables.%20Just%20a%20handful%20in%20a%20sandwich%20can%20quietly%20boost%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20intake%20of%20vitamins%20A%2C%20C%2C%20and%20K.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMillets%3A%20Ancient%20grains%20for%20modern%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20microgreens%20are%20the%20newcomers%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314758%2Fmothers-start-rigdam-foods-ready-to-eat-millet-snacks-for-children-earn-turnover-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillets%20are%20the%20wise%20elders%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20a%20comeback.%20For%20centuries%2C%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20laddoos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%20rotis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20khichdi%20%3C%2Fem%3Efilled%20Indian%20plates.%20Then%2C%20as%20polished%20rice%20and%20packaged%20cereals%20gained%20popularity%2C%20millets%20slipped%20into%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20returning%2C%20not%20as%20%E2%80%9Csuperfoods%20of%20the%20West%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20as%20staples%20with%20deep%20Indian%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20all%20know%2C%20mill